data.description: NOTE: THIS HAS AN ASSUMABLE FHA NOTE AT 4.5% Just look at ttheseprivate beautiful rear and side yards with lots of space to create your horseshoe pit,  entertainment area, or add pool.  Come back as the owner has made additional improvements with paint and carpet. For the right offer, the owner will consider giving a $1,500 flooring allowance for the upper level. One room was already upgraded with new carpeting and the recreation room was completely redone!  Need another bedroom and bath?  The lower level has rough in for additional bath. Fabulous new colonial features: 5yr old Roof and Windows, 2yr old Refrigerator, New Dishwasher, 6yr old Stove, and more.  This home has a beautiful hardwood floor, fireplace, eat-in kitchen, pantry, and rear deck that backs to woods, private.  The lower level has been freshly painted with newly installed carpeting,  a walk-out to the rear yard, a family room with fireplace, storage, office /hobby / or another bedroom, rough-in plumbing for an additional bathroom, and you could add a 4th bedroom.  The upper level features 3 big bedrooms and big closets, linen closets, and 2 full bathrooms.
